MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: The THVST_INV_SNAP_REL(Target table) holds Harvest Invoice Snapshot Relation details for each vendor in BI Data Mart to generate reports.
MAPPING.NAME: m_SCD_THVST_INV_SNAP_REL

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: If TQ.OOB_CD is null, then HVST_OOB_IN port will return default value as '0'
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: HVST_OOB_IN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, '00000000000000' AS INV_ID,/*for allocation always 14 zeros*/ 1 AS RTRVL_TYP_CD, /*for allocation always 1*/ TM.CORP_CD, MAX(TD.STAT_CD) STAT_CD, TQ.OOB_CD, TD.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD, CASE WHEN R.RPT_TYP_CD=26 THEN 2 ELSE 1 END AS HVST_TYP_CD, -1 AS INV_STUS_CD, MAX(TD.UPDT_TS) UPDT_TS FROM VRAP.TSNAP T INNER JOIN VRAP.TSNAP_DTL TD ON T.SNAP_ID=TD.SNAP_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THARVEST_QUE TQ ON TD.HVST_ID=TQ.HVST_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT R ON TQ.RPT_ID = R.RPT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY H ON R.HRCY_ID=H.HRCY_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TM ON T.MODEL_TYP_CD = TM.MODEL_TYP_CD WHERE TD.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_Allocation') AND H.HRCY_TYP_CD=3 GROUP BY TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, TM.CORP_CD, TQ.OOB_CD, TD.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD, R.RPT_TYP_CD WITH UR

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Consolidate all the Records from Invoice and Allocation
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Un_Allocation_Invoice

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Route new and changed records based on NEW_FLAG and CHANGED_FLAG
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Rtr_New_Changed_Rows_THVST_INV_SNAP_REL

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Check if source row exist in target table 1) If the record is present, then compare the column values of source and target. If there is a difference then set CHANGE_FLAG = 1 to denote it as changed record else CHANGE_FLAG = 0 2) If the record isn't present then set NEW_FLAG=1 to denote as new record.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Exp_Detect_Changes_THVST_INV_SNAP_REL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(Tgt_HVST_ID) OR ISNULL(Tgt_SNAP_ID) OR ISNULL(Tgt_INV_ID) OR ISNULL(Tgt_RTRVL_TYP_CD) OR ISNULL(Tgt_CORP_OWNR_ID),1,0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: NEW_FLAG

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(Tgt_HVST_ID) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_SNAP_ID ) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_INV_ID ) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_RTRVL_TYP_CD) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_CORP_OWNR_ID) AND ( Tgt_HVST_ACTV_IN!=Src_HVST_ACTV_IN or Tgt_HVST_OOB_IN!=Src_HVST_OOB_IN or Tgt_HVST_RPT_STUS_CD!=Src_HVST_RPT_STUS_CD or Tgt_HVST_TYP_CD!=Src_HVST_TYP_CD or Tgt_INV_STUS_CD!=Src_INV_STUS_CD), 1, 0 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: CHANGED_FLAG

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, TD.INV_ID, 2 AS RTRVL_TYP_CD, TM.CORP_CD, 1 AS HVST_ACTV_IN, COALESCE(TQ.OOB_CD,0) AS HVST_OOB_IN, 1 AS HVST_RPT_STUS_CD, CASE WHEN R.RPT_TYP_CD=26 THEN 2 ELSE 1 END AS HVST_TYP_CD, TD.INV_STAT_CD, MAX(TD.UPDT_TS) AS UPDT_TS FROM VRAP.TSNAP T INNER JOIN VRAP.TSNAP_INV_DTL TD ON T.SNAP_ID=TD.SNAP_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THARVEST_QUE TQ ON TD.HVST_ID=TQ.HVST_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT R ON TQ.RPT_ID = R.RPT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY H ON R.HRCY_ID=H.HRCY_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TM ON T.MODEL_TYP_CD = TM.MODEL_TYP_CD WHERE TD.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_Invoice') AND H.HRCY_TYP_CD=3 GROUP BY TD.HVST_ID, TD.SNAP_ID, TD.INV_ID, TM.CORP_CD, COALESCE(TQ.OOB_CD,0), R.RPT_TYP_CD, TD.INV_STAT_CD WITH UR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: HVST_ID = In_HVST_ID AND SNAP_ID = In_SNAP_ID AND INV_ID = In_INV_ID AND RTRVL_TYP_CD = In_RTRVL_TYP_CD AND CORP_OWNR_ID = In_CORP_OWNR_ID
